title: Missing Documentation: Multiple links return 404 in Python API Guide
body_html:
Please make sure that this is a documentation issue. As per our GitHub Policy, we only address code/doc bugs, performance issues, feature requests and build/installation issues on GitHub. tag:doc_template

System information

  • TensorFlow version: Version 2.0

  • Doc Link: The following docs all have links that return a 404 error:

    • tensorflow/contrib/util/__init__.py
      • https://www.tensorflow.org/api_guides/python/contrib.util
    • tensorflow/python/lib/io/python_io.py
      • https://www.tensorflow.org/api_guides/python/python_io

    • tensorflow/core/api_def/base_api/api_def_SparseSegmentSum.pbtxt
